import React from 'react';
import { FC } from "react";
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'
import Col from "react-bootstrap/Col";
import Row from "react-bootstrap/Row";



export const PartnerScreen : FC = () => {

return(
<Form>
  <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formPlaintextCompanyName">
    <Form.Label column sm="2">
      Название компании
    </Form.Label>
    <Col sm="10">
      <Form.Control plaintext readOnly defaultValue="ООО Астра" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Group>
  <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formPlaintextFoundationYear">
    <Form.Label column sm="2">
      Год основания
    </Form.Label>
    <Col sm="10">
      <Form.Control plaintext readOnly defaultValue="2010" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Group>
  <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formPlaintextNumEmployees">
    <Form.Label column sm="2">
      Количество сотрудников
    </Form.Label>
    <Col sm="10">
      <Form.Control plaintext readOnly defaultValue="8" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Group>
</Form>

)


    
}
